-- Netflix shares up 2.5 percent on news of iPhone app
-- 
-- Mon Jun 7, 2010 1:28pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/06/07/us-markets-stocks-netflix-idUSTRE6564AF20100607

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Netflix Inc briefly extended their gains to 2.5 percent in afternoon trading on Monday after the company said it would bring a free app to Apple Inc's iPhone product this summer. 

